{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究一定质量的气体在体积不变时，压强与温度的关系。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理想气体的状态方程：<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">p</span></em></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">V</span></em>/<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>T</em></span>=<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">常数。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">压强传感器、温度传感器、烧杯、铁架台、石棉网、酒精灯、火柴、试管</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.点燃酒精灯；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.点击表单中的</span>&ldquo;记录&rdquo;按钮；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.每间隔一段时间，点击一次</span>&ldquo;记录&rdquo;按钮；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.点击绘图按钮，得到压强与温度的图线；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.观察图线，得出结论。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一定质量的气体在体积不变时，压强与热力学温度成正比。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一定质量的理想气体</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>pV</em></span>/<em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">T</span></em>=<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">常数。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}